name: Kaylin Slevin
description:
v1: This inversion of Kaylin Slevin (Instagram Bimbo) was trained on 18 images (including flipped ones) at 2600 steps on v1.5-pruned and pairs very well with Fake Lips: https://civitai.com/models/18264 for a bit of 'authenticity'. v1 vector tokens were set to 8 so you may need to (full body:1.6) or more to get past south of her navel in your pics. Best results at 768x768. Best placed early in prompt for accuracy. (note in the second 768x1024 pic her iris' are InPainted blue)

v2: Trained at 2550 steps at a variable rate on v1.5-pruned, more consistent across a range of checkpoints. Same dataset as V1 but upscaled and refined more carefully with less vector tokens making her more flexible when using text2img.

If you like and care to help me pay off the 3080 chugging away before me you can kick some sand in my face here: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/admiralundr

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description: Same dataset upscaled, lower vectors to make it more flexible and consistent across checkpoints
